      <title>特朗普谴责纽约欺诈案裁决，处罚迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/trump-decries-new-york-fraud-case-ruling-as-penalties-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普誓言将对纽约法官对其商业行为处以的 3.64 亿美元罚款提出上诉，并在 2024 年关键的战场州密歇根州召集支持者时，谴责他日益严重的法律困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/trump-decries-new-york-fraud-case-ruling-as-penalties-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 03:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过近一周的抗议后，印度农民准备进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/indian-farmers-gear-up-for-talks-after-almost-week-of-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度北部数万名种植者抗议近一周后，印度农民将于周日与政府举行另一轮会谈，以帮助结束农作物价格争端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/indian-farmers-gear-up-for-talks-after-almost-week-of-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国前领导人他信假释出狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/former-thai-premier-thaksin-shinawatra-freed-from-detention-under-parole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前总理他信·西那瓦 (Thaksin Shinawatra) 周日被释放，由其家人支持的政党领导的联合政府以他年老和患病为由给予他特别假释。]]></description>
